    "advancement": [],
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em data-start=\"591\" data-end=\"624\">11th-level Shadow Lords feature</em></p><p data-start=\"626\" data-end=\"657\">You remain unshaken amid chaos.</p><p data-start=\"659\" data-end=\"739\">You gain advantage on saving throws against being <strong data-start=\"709\" data-end=\"720\">charmed</strong> or <strong data-start=\"724\" data-end=\"738\">frightened</strong>.</p><p data-start=\"741\" data-end=\"984\">In addition, <strong data-start=\"754\" data-end=\"785\">once per short or long rest</strong>, when you <strong data-start=\"796\" data-end=\"825\">succeed on a saving throw</strong>, you may choose one creature within <strong data-start=\"862\" data-end=\"873\">30 feet</strong> that you can see. That creature has <strong data-start=\"910\" data-end=\"951\">disadvantage on its next saving throw</strong> before the end of its next turn.</p>",
